WEBVTT

16:53.297 --> 16:56.731
to suffer for the sins
of ordinary people?

16:56.733 --> 16:58.433
Because He loves us.

16:59.535 --> 17:02.170
God made Himself
approachable to us,

17:02.172 --> 17:05.073
human,
so we could understand Him.

17:05.075 --> 17:07.742
We can't understand God
in all His perfection.
